Riley et al.35 developed an empirical relation (Eq. 3) that relates the effective diffusion coefficient Deff to the local free diffusion coefficient D0, the intracellular diffusion coefficient Dcell and the cell volume fraction φ. This equation, based on Monte Carlo simulations, shows a good agreement with available data throughout a wide range of cell volume fractions (0.04 < φ < 0.95). 3\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
